translations: n．米格（Mig）：苏联及后来的俄罗斯制造的一系列战斗机，全名为米高扬·古列维奇·米格（Mikoyan-Gurevich MiG）。

sentences.sentence: Dogfight against MiGs! Cold War jet air-combat game on the go!
sentences.translation: 混战对抗米格！冷战飞机空战游戏去吧！

sentences.sentence: India needs to stop flying MIGs which has claimed more lives during peace time.
sentences.translation: 在这和平年代还要了这么多人性命，印度应该停飞米格战机！
